Package com.sri.ai.grinder.library

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Associative  
    BindingTopSimplifier
    A Switch rewriter replacing symbols by their bound value from context, if any.
    CommutativeAssociative
    Implements the basics for commutative, associative operators with a neutral element such as addition, multiplication, conjunction, etc.
    CommutativeAssociativeOnNumbers
    Utility methods for CommutativeAssociative operations on numerical expressions.
    CommutativeAssociativeWithOperationOnJavaConstantsOnly
    Specializes CommutativeAssociative to situations in which all arguments are constants, reducing the whole expression to a constant itself.
    Disequality
    Implements disequality.
    Equality
    Implements equality.
    FormulaUtil
    A collection of utility routines specific to formulas.
    FunctorConstants  
    IsVariable
    A Predicate that determines if a given Expression represents a Variable.
    SyntacticSubstitute
    A class providing a static method for substituting symbols or function applications in an expression by another expression (not subject itself to the same substitution, which would either not occur or lead to an infinite recursion).
